1. *Hladna* voda mi je mnogo prijala nakon dugog trčanja. (Cold water felt great to me after a long run.)
2. Ovo jelo se najbolje služi kad je *hladno*. (This dish is best served when it's cold.)
3. *Hladnoća* je prodrla kroz moju jaknu. (The coldness penetrated through my jacket.)
4. Ne bih želeo da spavam u *hladnoj* sobi. (I wouldn't want to sleep in a cold room.)
5. *Hladnim* rukama nisam mogao da držim olovku. (I couldn't hold the pen with my cold hands.)
6. *Hladan* vetar je duvao ceo dan. (A cold wind blew all day.)
7. Na plaži je bilo *hladno* pa smo se vratili u hotel. (It was cold at the beach, so we returned to the hotel.)
8. *Hladnoćom* sam se tresao dok sam čekao na autobus. (I was shivering from the cold while waiting for the bus.)
9. *Hladna* atmosfera u sobi me činila nervoznim. (The cold atmosphere in the room made me nervous.)
10. Još uvek se sećam *hladnog* pogleda koji mi je uputila. (I still remember the cold look she gave me.)